Package weka.classifiers.collective.meta

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdvancedCollective
    Uses collective classification (cf.
    Chopper
    Collective Classifier that uses one classifier for labeling the test data after training on the train set.
    CollectiveEM
    The given base classifier trains on the training set and then labels the instances of the test set.
    CollectiveNeighbor
    Dummy classifier for TwoStageCollective - only used to keep experiments working!

    Valid options are:

    CollectiveWrapper
    Represents a wrapper around any normal WEKA classifier.
    FilteredCollectiveClassifier
    A meta classifier that takes a filter and a collective classifier as input.
    The filter is only trained on the provided training set, but still applied to instances from the training and test set, as well as to any instance that gets passed to the meta classifier.
    SimpleCollective
    Uses collective classification (cf.
    TwoStageCollective
    Collective Classifier that uses one classifier (first "-B") for labeling the test data after training on the train set.
    Weighting
    Collective Classifier that uses one classifier for labeling the test data after training on the train set.
    YATSI
    "Yet Another Two Stage Idea" - A collective Classifier that uses the given classifier to train on the training set and labeling the unlabeled data.
